Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}格力高：也就是日本江崎格力高食品公司，著名產品有pocky，相信大家不會陌生。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,pi～ne～app～le～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我來嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  一層一層上可是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格～力～高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的附～贈～品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能擅自加字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不是一般都要加個贈品的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50比50
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你要是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要發動自己的規則了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭•剪刀•布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一個輪到麻衣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちよた　みけら　はとほ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,らすて　のはて　きらと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なりは　してと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:19.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注釋見後文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是復活的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧鐘停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…媽媽真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過7點鐘要把我喊起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和街道委員會的人們去玩藤球了  by媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}藤球：由東南亞的"sepak raga"運動起源的用頭和腳傳遞使球不落地的運動。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤…藤球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.56,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N5
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  今天可是我值日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧鐘為什麼偏偏今天就沒有電池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完了的話就應該提前跟我說「用完了」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨蛋鬧鐘！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之只能以全速跑過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:04:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話總會有辦法…話說回來  剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個很奇怪的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它…追來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀什麼呀  這場賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要追我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  稍微打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個木魚是你掉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這個金木魚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被殺掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配合的話  就要被殺掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我是隻熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有時候我…還是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我的真面目是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘  正確答案是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我穿著美緒的校服所以沒認出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  難得一大早就能看到如此漂亮的飛旋拳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  真的非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我可是累死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把那個鬧鐘弄停可費了大勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  別那麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我來請你吃拉麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是野口英世，印在1000円上的日本著名醫學家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的野口！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.20,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,250)\fad(600,0)}咒\N語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所謂的咒語其實是FC上用來代替存檔的密碼，且正確的密碼其實是\Nちよた みけら はとほ らすて のはて きらと なには してと，來源於DQ2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,220)}咒語輸入錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:53.86,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N6
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鯊魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  那片雲  好像鯊魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  哪一片？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我牛奶買回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…4.5  4.5的純牛奶  4.5的純牛奶  4.5！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}好  是特濃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}但是怎麼了  突然間想喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有夾心蛋糕卷可以吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,335)}roll cake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以隨便地改造我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夾心蛋糕卷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！  4.5的純牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼4.5的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得手臂裡裝著夾心蛋糕卷而生活下去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈  涼涼的好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要是這被外面的誰看到了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕咕嚕咕嚕～咕嚕嚕～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  也給我喝一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  夾心蛋糕卷也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}甜麵包：日文叫做「甘食」，甜味的傘狀麵包。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  就給你吃點甜麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  我按錯鍵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你又要做這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不小心在外面啟動了的話會變成什麼樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}桑勃：源自俄羅斯的格鬥技，類似柔道，也加入了擒拿術等綜合格鬥技。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑勃摔跤指揮官真是太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你加個音樂播放機能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢  為什麼要向改造方向發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好聽我說話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足的一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  因為博士你已經吃了夾心蛋糕卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你好了  反正我還有年輪蛋糕可以吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:18.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,335)}Baumkuchen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道又在我的身體裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還是下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請一開始就全部放到冰箱裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你滿滿的能量喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美緒～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笑臉是要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道又忘記做作業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這可真是不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  總是這樣話考試又會很慘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次  就這次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一次了  拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  之前你就已經說過這話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士絕不食言！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你早就已經食言了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這次了哦  真的最後一次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我能仰仗的就只有美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  剛才我說的做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我抄好了的話就馬上還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  讓我看讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  我是不是忘記什麼東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上做完作業後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完作業後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨手畫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨手畫的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不允許你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:39.52,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,300)\fad(600,600)\bord10\shad0\be50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我自己也忘了寫作業了  真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  把筆記還給我吧  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  我都說了看了也沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來又來  真是的  別耍那一套了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過下次我一定會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難辦了  這下可慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是看到那個的話  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會被奇怪的眼光看待的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且看到那幅畫的人  偏偏是祐子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那種傳播力可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音速級別！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  那…那是國語的筆記本  數學的在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本子上：數學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:53.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本子上：每日日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這上面寫了是數學的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我肚子很痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會抄好的  稍微等一下下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了  要是在這裡被看到的話  我就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中生活就結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  那本筆記  我用一千円買！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  不是那樣  那本筆記會…  那本筆記會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會爆炸啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追不上奔跑著的祐子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了  我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:16:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  我的人生  到現在都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有些不如意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總的來說  是場幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都完了  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生…和男人們的盛宴一起結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對！不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒…生命吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}暫停成功\N「ナタデココ」椰漿果凍，椰子汁發酵的凝膠狀食品起源於菲律賓，也是演員水沢奈子的愛稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這裡奔跑的場景人物線條用的都是原作裡的作畫風格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣…我也夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在…走廊上奔跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從後面把筆記傳上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有忘記寫作業的傢伙們快點自己承認哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一時間還真不知道會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好總算是平安無事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就能回到我的日常生活了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是忘記擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  長野原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}目標：伴著汗水的無悔青春  1年Q班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我忘記寫作業了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.31,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,300)\fad(600,0)}收\N拾\N屋\N子\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  請稍微收拾下屋子裡的垃圾好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對博士來說這或許還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:09.14,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,300)\fad(0,600)}學\N生\N指\N導
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那時候  我對那傢伙說了3999…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  抱歉  安中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:23.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在走廊上請勿急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是有一點點啦  你的發飾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太大了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像兔子一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.49,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,280)\fad(0,0)}甜\N面\N包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜麵包真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}便利店招牌：春季的筆頭草便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}商品售罄  令人懷念的甜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}店長推薦：廉價裝甜麵包，大人氣，多到突破天際的分量，55個裝，超好吃。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.22,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原  你有沒有作為文化祭執行委員的自覺啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微認真地考慮下會怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都非常認真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為戲劇部部長就要經常融入各色角色之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不知道嗎  立花美里喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂你個頭啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}好好聽我說話!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上我們差不多該決定文化祭的擺攤事項了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的戲劇部一點關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換商標了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我和這傢伙分到一組了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍道部的比賽也要臨近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}Helvetica Standard日常原作者あらゐけいいち以自己的同人社團「ヒマラヤイルカ」的名義創作的同人志\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  現在真不想當什麼文化祭執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:08.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}翹起小指是笹原的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  還看什麼漫畫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快點提出方案的話  我們不都回不了家了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  因為是新刊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒有一個方案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前提出的葡萄酒品嘗大賽不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行  駁回喲  駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級駁回！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  笹原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  剛才開始就在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我稍微有點用腦過度想不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  笹原  你要去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去趟廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來她今天的心情相當不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說葡萄酒品嘗大賽已經是非常完美的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那傢伙從開始到現在完全都沒有提出方案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我這樣和她說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會沒命的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是如果我不提出方案的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就沒辦法回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非得要我把思考方式降到庶民級別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我就稍微認真地考慮下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你可沒有任何意思哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
